name: The Nymphs of the Asphalt V2

metadata.name: Asphalt Nymphs - F1 01 - Aiza Adams
metadata.description:
Watch the promo:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QJjmotOUmxA

The semi-decomposed shells and their contents, imprisoned in otherworldly diapositives, form a caustic humus that fuels the higher strata with toxic vapors. Downtrodden by their humiliating fate, these Nymphs sink into the bowels of the earth, firmly sheltered by the indifferent parent rock. Itâ€™s covered by heavy sheets of soil that resemble red velvet generously anointed with a thick layer of nutritious humus. Cracked relic slabs, decorated with scarce unidentifiable ornaments, act as frosting on top. Together, these disjointed segments form a single multi-layered foundation for the Perfect Canvas of Metaphysical Asphalt, upon which the Enigmatic Master frantically tap-dances, disturbing the tangled bonds between the fragile covers over the abyss.
